---

---

<section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-md md:max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-6 tracking-wide text-[#544A40]">
            レッスン料金・システム
        </h2>
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-[#A88B58] text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] font-serif uppercase"
        >
            <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/40"></div>
            Fees & System
            <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/40"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div
        class="bg-[#FCFAF7] p-8 md:p-12 border border-[#EAE3DA] shadow-sm text-center w-[90%] max-w-sm md:max-w-3xl mx-auto relative rounded-2xl"
    >
        <div class="mb-10 font-serif text-[#544A40]">
            <p class="mb-10 text-[13px] tracking-[0.25em] text-[#544A40] opacity-80">
                - 1レッスンあたりの料金 -
            </p>
            <div
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-stretch gap-10 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12"
            >
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center relative md:w-1/3"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-[13px] text-[#A88B58] mb-3 tracking-widest font-medium"
                        >30分レッスン</span
                    >
                    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                            >5,000</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-[#544A40] ml-1 opacity-80"
                            >円</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[13px] text-[#6B5F54] leading-loose text-center opacity-90">
                        <span class="inline-block">初心者の方・</span><span class="inline-block">まずは基礎から確認したい方・</span><span class="inline-block">短時間からスタートしたい方に。</span>
                    </p>
                    <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-[#A88B58]/20 mx-auto mt-8 md:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center relative md:w-1/3"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-[13px] text-[#A88B58] mb-3 tracking-widest font-medium"
                        >45分レッスン</span
                    >
                    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                            >7,500</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-[#544A40] ml-1 opacity-80"
                            >円</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[13px] text-[#6B5F54] leading-loose text-center opacity-90">
                        <span class="inline-block">久しぶりにピアノを再開する方・</span><span class="inline-block">趣味として自分のペースで</span><span class="inline-block">続けたい方におすすめ。</span>
                    </p>
                    <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-[#A88B58]/20 mx-auto mt-8 md:hidden"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center relative md:w-1/3"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-[13px] text-[#A88B58] mb-3 tracking-widest font-medium"
                        >60分レッスン</span
                    >
                    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="text-3xl font-medium font-serif text-[#544A40]"
                            >10,000</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-[#544A40] ml-1 opacity-80"
                            >円</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[13px] text-[#6B5F54] leading-loose text-center opacity-90">
                        <span class="inline-block">好きな曲を仕上げたい方・</span><span class="inline-block">表現力やペダリングまで</span><span class="inline-block">じっくり指導を受けたい方に。</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p
            class="text-[12px] md:text-[13px] leading-loose tracking-wide mb-10 text-[#6B5F54] text-left md:text-center mx-auto"
        >
            ※ご自宅または近隣のレンタルスタジオで受講いただける個人レッスンです（出張費・交通費込み）。<br />
            月1回から受講可能。目標や進め方を相談しながら進めるマンツーマンレッスンです。
        </p>
        <a
            href="/lesson"
            class="inline-block border border-[#A88B58] text-[#A88B58] px-12 py-4 hover:bg-[#A88B58]/5 transition-all text-[13px] tracking-[0.2em] font-medium"
        >
            詳しい料金プランを見る
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
